   <h3>Guidelines for collaborating with 
    someone with a disability</h3>
    <ol>
     <li>If you don't know what to do, ask</li>
     <li>Treat each other the way you would want to be 
      treated</li>
      <li>Focus on the person</li>
      <li>Don't touch service animals or assistive devices 
       without permission</li>
      <li>Pay attention to how you interact to avoid 
       excluding others</li>
    </ol>
   <h3>Accommodations</h3>
   <span>Common accommodations include:</span>
